For those of you who would like to finish the story arc, you can find it on WebToons starting here;  https://www.webtoons.com/en/canvas/pixie-and-brutus/the-long-story-part-1/viewer?title_no=452175&episode_no=135

For anyone curious, my Birthday went well enough yesterday. A lot of pain to deal with, but I had tacos for dinner so can't complain about that. The rest was spent trying not to move too much and getting in a few rounds of gaming with my buddy.

I hope that things will settle down, that the site will be fixed, and that we can all put this behind us soon enough... Unfortunately, until the dust settles we won't know for sure. You have all (or most of you at least) been a wonderful community, and I hope to see you all at the end of this.

The Unnamed Poet, signing off.... For now?

Quick Edit:  Be sure to check your DMs! With the notifications not working, be sure you check your chat messages for anything important, while that functionality still works!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wsX1eoX</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheUnnamedPoet]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Medialab HQ right now.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ULHYx0Y</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QyhjwJD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ULHYx0Y</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TacticoolWolf]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Doing my part</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1SOcori</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tUYDtXZ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/1SOcori</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Saici]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Free Speech!!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Z9aikLm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jOuvCcm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Free Speech and lock up pedophiles!!!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Z9aikLm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LadyYorkshire]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Been coming to imgur for decades for my serotonin treats and weird culture, corporations don't get to be offended when they are perceived</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2OVylPW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QzVvfAw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2OVylPW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tharasyn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>sequi pecuniam</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CkTAulx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rHwbA